{"prompt": "Generate a website for a renewable energy startup. The design should be forward-thinking, with a bold yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Aura Energy</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #FFDA63; /* Bold Yellow */\n            --secondary-color: #FDF3C1; /* Lighter Yellow/Cream */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #FFFFFF;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: #333333;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #333333;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #555555;\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .services h2, .about h2, .contact h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n        }\n\n        .about-content {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 40px;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .about-text {\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n\n        .about-image {\n            flex: 1;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .about-image img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            display: grid;\n            gap: 15px;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin-left: auto;\n            margin-right: auto;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea {\n            padding: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #cccccc;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            width: 100%;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border: none;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #e6c351;\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333333;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Aura Energy</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#services\">Our Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Powering a Brighter Future.</h2>\n        <p>Aura Energy is dedicated to providing innovative and sustainable energy solutions for a cleaner planet. We harness the power of nature to bring you reliable and eco-friendly energy.</p>\n        <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get a Free Quote</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Our Services</h2>\n        <div class=\"services-grid\">\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Solar Solutions</h3>\n                <p>Cutting-edge solar panel installations for homes and businesses. Maximize your energy independence.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Wind Power</h3>\n                <p>Harnessing the wind's potential with efficient turbine technology. Sustainable energy for large-scale needs.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Energy Storage</h3>\n                <p>Advanced battery solutions to store your renewable energy. Ensure power availability when you need it.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>About Aura Energy</h2>\n        <div class=\"about-content\">\n            <div class=\"about-text\">\n                <p>Founded on the principle of environmental stewardship, Aura Energy is a leader in the renewable energy sector. We believe in a future powered by clean, sustainable sources. Our team of experts is committed to delivering personalized solutions that meet your unique energy needs while minimizing your carbon footprint.</p>\n                <p>We strive for innovation, efficiency, and a positive impact on our planet. Join us in building a sustainable tomorrow.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"about-image\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/FFDA63/333333?text=Sustainable+Future\" alt=\"Illustration of renewable energy\">\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <p>Ready to switch to clean energy? Contact us today for a consultation!</p>\n        <form class=\"contact-form\">\n            <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n            <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n            <input type=\"tel\" placeholder=\"Your Phone Number\">\n            <textarea placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"6\" required></textarea>\n            <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n        </form>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Aura Energy. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}